OL,3,CMan aged 20 killed in Easter Sunday
OL,4,Ccrash
OL,6,FA 20-year-old man has died following a
OL,7,Fcrash in Co Antrim.
OL,9,FThe man, who was from the Crossgar
OL,10,Farea in Co Down, was taken to hospital
OL,11,Fafter the early morning crash on
OL,12,FEaster Sunday.
OL,14,FHe was later pronounced dead.
OL,16,FThe Police Service of Northern Ireland
OL,17,Fsaid they were alerted to the grey BMW
OL,18,Fcrash on the Castlecat Road, Dervock,
OL,19,Fshortly before 1 AM.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G1/4
