OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F448A1775657466
OL,3,CMan aged 20 killed in Easter Sunday
OL,4,Ccrash
OL,6,FThe road was closed overnight for
OL,7,Fenquiries but has since reopened.
OL,9,FTwenty-one people have lost their
OL,10,Flives on the roads so far this year
OL,11,Fwhich is more than double the number
OL,12,Fduring the same period in 2025.
OL,14,FDetective Inspector Stewart from the
OL,15,FCollision Investigation Unit said:
OL,16,F"Officers attended alongside emergency
OL,17,Fpartners, and the male driver, who was
OL,18,Faged 20 and from the Crossgar area,
OL,19,Fwas taken to hospital for treatment
OL,20,Ffor his injuries, where he sadly
OL,21,Fpassed away.
