OL,3,CMan aged 20 killed in Easter Sunday
OL,4,Ccrash
OL,6,F"Our enquiries are continuing, and we
OL,7,Fwould appeal to anyone who witnessed
OL,8,Fthe collision, or who may have digital
OL,9,Ffootage which could assist with our
OL,10,Finvestigation, to contact the
OL,11,FCollision Investigation Unit on 101,
OL,12,Fquoting reference number 76 of 05/04/
OL,13,F26."
